    "description": "Encourage Technologies Co., Ltd. develops, maintains, and sells computer system software products primarily in Japan. It offers ESS SmartIT Operation products, including ESS REC, a standard tool for monitoring and auditing user system operations; ESS FileGate, which provides a safe file transfer environment through various types of file sanitization technologies; ESS AdminONE, a privileged ID management product; ESS AdminControl for Client, for managing local administrator passwords; ID Inspector, which identifies users who utilize shared IDs, such as root/administrators, without any customization of applications and operating systems; and ESS AutoQuality, a user system operation solution. The company also provides BPO and consulting services related to computer operation management. In addition, it offers solutions for ransomware, IT control, privileged ID management, evidence management, outsourcing, work style reform, BCP measures, telework visualization, PCI DSS, and RPA control monitoring for the finance, cloud, medical care, and local government sectors. Encourage Technologies Co., Ltd. was incorporated in 2002 and is headquartered in Chuo, Japan."
